            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Harol!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sophie? What is it...? Did something happen?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Nope. It's just that you helped us out a lot, so I wanted to properly thank you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Thank me...? I don't recall doing anything worthy of thanks..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "That's not true."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...I see. Well, I'm just glad I could help."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Do you think I could get stronger if I used guns too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You? Use guns? Haha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hey! Why are you laughing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It's just that I don't think they'd suit you very well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Grr."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You already have a great power called alchemy. There's no need for you to use guns."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I... Guess so?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, that's right. Anyway, I'm sure you're tired. You should go back to your atelier and rest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay. I'll do that. See you again, Harol!"
        }
    ]
}